  "instructions": [
    "Whisk together amazake and lemon juice in a small bowl.",
    "In a large skillet, heat olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add sliced red onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add sliced fennel and cook for an additional 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in artichoke hearts, olives, parsley, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, until heated through.",
    "Meanwhile, slice the shio-koji-cured salmon into thin pieces.",
    "To assemble the bowls, place a scoop of cooked brown rice on the bottom, followed by a piece of salmon, then the onion-fennel mixture, and finally a sprinkle of crushed fennel seeds if using.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
